516
00:20:57,714 --> 00:21:01,426
GOB PROTESTS THE PET STORE'S 
FROZEN DOVE EXCHANGE POLICY.

517
00:21:01,426 --> 00:21:03,928
- RETURN FROM WHENCE YOU CAME.

518
00:21:03,928 --> 00:21:05,972
AND, MICHAEL, 
REALIZING THE BANANA STAND

519
00:21:05,972 --> 00:21:08,600
IS THE ONLY PROFITABLE PART 
OF THE BLUTH EMPIRE,

520
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,269
DECIDES TO REBUILD.

521
00:21:10,269 --> 00:21:12,145
- YOU COULDN'T HAVE CALLED ME?

522
00:21:12,145 --> 00:21:14,939
I CAN'T SWING A HAMMER?

523
00:21:14,939 --> 00:21:16,441
- I GOT A RABBIT TO BUY.
